column2: Function of Myc in Mouse Lung Tumours

This is a subset analysis of main analysis Myc. In this sub-analysis clusters C7 and C12 from analysis Myc Main Analysis V3 Dec 2022 were selected. Due to the small cell numbers for some samples, cells are aggregated by sample group rather than by sample prior to integration.
